{"tid":1558630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地需要多at least 一倍時間 爭取餘下訴求！不被捕先能夠達至可持續抗爭！三大要點！","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:31:31.000Z","uid":66390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"914ae6476752a939e686eb09fc5f0e06c2345359","tid":1558630,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 大家問心<br />\n相對較易一定係「撤例」<br />\n但都搞成3個月 拉成千幾個 傷左幾百個<br />\n<br />\n餘下訴求<br />\n必須以<span style=\"color: orange;\">雙普選為首項</span><br />\n普選先係終極目標<br />\n<br />\n就算呢家有獨立調查委員會 大家會收貨咩？<br />\n未有雙普選 甚至香港獨立<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">抗爭必須繼續</span><br />\n<br />\n有左<span style=\"color: orange;\">雙普選</span><br />\n其實訴求話都無咁易啦<br />\n普選埋立法會<br />\n你鐘意cut差佬人工就cut<br />\n你鐘意送佢地去大灣區就送<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以雙普選必須為首項訴求</span><br />\n而大家要有心理準備<br />\n一定會以呢家計<br />\n最少打多3個月（當然唔止啦）<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得<span style=\"color: orange;\">我要真普選</span>有膠味<br />\n今日我地以勇武方式爭取真普選就唔膠<br />\n<br />\n時間唔係問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕 受傷人數先係問題</span><br />\n來緊必須大大下降<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以戀戰 但你唔可以被捕<br />\n每次大戰 <br />\n請確保：<br />\n1. 有冇空間走（後排夠唔夠鬆）<br />\n2. 有冇被包 （自己組team 有自己既哨）<br />\n3. 有冇車返屋企（除左巴士 黨鐵 搵定安全地方比自己team走 再搵家長車）<br />\n<br />\n總之 來緊抗爭好簡單<br />\n堅持同埋不受傷不被捕<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係 前線只會愈來愈少<br />\n而條路會愈來愈行 會輸！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不被捕先能夠達至可持續抗爭</span>"},{"pid":"faa9dfeceda4c44d27b2162da999b46f9ac21141","tid":1558630,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"不被捕先能夠達至可持續抗爭"},{"pid":"323a68814c6fb4bd9b567e5e4076d5d58b119986","tid":1558630,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4636791014abf51d3b6bbfa97d094e88320d41ed","tid":1558630,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"686ceb8a0eb39d0c6c2393c913748d8b03666ef0","tid":1558630,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73b17cfee6bdab88d30ef8ae5bd83dcf3dc470a8","tid":1558630,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3281f5a932a7260da97be48e3e8f081a5ed8ddda","tid":1558630,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"9.15 民陣遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年9月15日（日）<br />\n時間：下午 3:00 起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n遊行路線：從銅鑼灣東角道起步，遊行至遮打道行人專用區"}]}